        "content": "# ü§ñ Simple AI Chatbot Using Google Drive Knowledge in n8n\n\nThis guide explains how to use an **AI chatbot powered by OpenAI**, where the knowledge comes from files (like PDFs, text, etc.) stored in **Google Drive**. No coding needed!\n\n---\n\n## üìå What This Workflow Does\n\n- Automatic file updates from Google Drive \n- Converts it into a searchable knowledge base (vector store)\n- Allows users to chat and ask questions about that file\n- AI replies based **only** on the content in your file!\n\n---",
